Solution: Extensions
In this reading, you will review the solution code for the exercise. The code block below outlines the outcome of the exercise in its entirety:

class Dish(   
val dishName: String,   
val ingredients: MutableList<String> )
fun Dish.printIngredients()
{     println(ingredients)
} 
fun Dish.removeSalt() 

{    
ingredients.remove("Salt") 
} 
fun main()
{     
val onionSoup = Dish("Onion Soup", mutableListOf("Onion", "Cheese", "Water", "Salt")) 
onionSoup.removeSalt()  
onionSoup.printIngredients()
}   
